query:
UPDATE contract_sign_requests
               SET provisioning_instance_details = $1,
                   provisioning_completed_at_ns = $2,
                   gateway_slug = $3,
                   gateway_subdomain = $4,
                   gateway_ssh_port = $5,
                   gateway_port_range_start = $6,
                   gateway_port_range_end = $7
               WHERE contract_id = $8
